  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b86\u0bb2\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Catholic Church in Gurunagar struck by lightning",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "While the Sunday Mass was being held at the Catholic Church in Gurunagar, Jaffna, there was a brief commotion due to a lightning strike.",
        "According to local residents, the incident took place at Gurunagar's St. Arogyanatha Temple at around 6.30 am on Sunday morning.",
        "The accident took place in several parts of Jaffna in the morning when rain accompanied by thunder and lightning was reported.",
        "Due to the lightning strike in the temple, roof parts and electrical connections were slightly damaged. However, the public reports that no one was harmed."
      ],
